<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2016-04-05</DATELINE><TITLE>Global Strategies for the Prevention and Control of Infectious Diseases and Non-Communicable Diseases</TITLE><BODY>This article on global health reviews the environment surrounding health strategies and plans, as well as lessons learned from the first 15 years of the 21st century, followed by a discussion on the quest for a new paradigm for disease control efforts and challenges and opportunities for Japan.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>